.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/914e643d4bb234e46ecd491c33b7dc43/2026-04/33_4.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"整體評分：3.92\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c7d67e28e52a27db159a703b746bfbcc/2026-04/34_1.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"本產品質地豐潤柔滑，易於塗抹。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/97934fb5ab1a333dd5a4cd15b8875c1f/2026-04/35_1.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"Ａ級PDRN精華液\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4ea6c15aac6da681f0ddc38fd39e7079/2026-04/36_1.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"第2位 A級（4.04分）：fractionalCC PDRN Shot 1000+ Toning Essence（日圓¥2200，約HK$108）\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/24d22570be6ceb662a77905eabda63b1/2026-04/37_1.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"整體評分：4.04\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/39f327dd580288d1e4012f68deee1300/2026-04/38_1.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"這款PDRN精華液質地柔滑，易於塗抹，呈凝膠狀。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ebe4abbc0f8b422a130a7e961656a444/2026-04/39_1.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"第1位 A級（4.46分）：NATURE REPUBLIC Black Renew PDRN Perfecting Essence（日圓¥2750，約HK$135）\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6db30b71cd1248c5a7d475df4a3be00d/2026-04/40_1.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"整體評分：4.46\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8a3258e830a793884ec18d3c8d10dceb/2026-04/41_1.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"這款產品蘊含源自魚子醬、黑酵母和黑蘿蔔的PDRN成分，在保濕測試中展現出卓越的保濕功效，有效提升肌膚含水量。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4126921aa0623c4ef7f0650f411da88e/2026-04/42_1.png\"/>\n</body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-04T15:29:03.518810+00:00","quality":{"score":3,"chars":1605,"images":76,"source":"星島頭條","fallback":"none"}}